{"title":"“小八路”的诗","authors":["黄水发","何佳汝"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":11,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“小八路”的诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修公路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄水发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同学们，来挑土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"准备修公路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把它修得更牢固，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保证物资快运输。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用老师喊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同学积极干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又唱歌又工作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家分工又合作。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大同学，扛石头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小同学来装篓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"准备打敌人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打得它抬不起头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮兵叔叔打得好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何佳汝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮兵叔叔打得好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万颗炮弹飞向金门岛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打得蒋军乱逃跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打得军营不见了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打得敌舰沉海底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打得敌机往下掉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人听了哈哈笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个称赞打得好。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}